Plan entity / manager

EntityManager (hydrate)
|
| -> ArticleManager (__construct() / addArticle() / getArticle() / editArticle() / deleteArticle())
|   -> Article (setter & getter => id / title / author / content / add_date)
|
| -> CommentManager (__construct() / addComment() / getComment() / editComment() / deleteComment())
|   -> Comment (setter & getter => id / title / author / content / add_date)
|
| -> UserManager (__construct() / addUser() / getUser() / editUser() / deleteUser())
|   -> User (setter & getter => id / username / plainPassword / password / salt / role)
